data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming area of southeast Conway! Open house on Sunday, November 5, from 2-4, and be sure to check out the video walkthrough! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this stylish corner lot property. Ideal for first-time home buyers, this residence offers everything you need and is move-in ready. Step into the fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or enjoying quiet relaxation. With a two-car garage, parking will never be an issue. Located in a desirable subdivision, you'll have easy access to a myriad of shopping and dining options. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own your own piece of paradise in southeast Conway! Entergy, Vilonia Water, Roof 2020, HVAC 2018, hot water heater 2020. Ask your agent to see the Seller's Property Disclosure that's on file. Call me or your favorite agent to schedule a showing! :)
